When Shobana @amplifiedsoul asked me to model for the morning show to help spotlight more South Asian talent and faces, it was an instant yes.

Growing up I would’ve never imagined turning on the TV and seeing someone who looked like me on screen.

Thank you Shobana for helping pave the way! I’ll always be here for brown girls supporting brown girls — for showing up, lifting each other up, and becoming the change we once dreamed of. 🩷
